<think>
The question asks which film has the director who died earlier between "Condemned Women" and "Faces In The Dark". I need to find out the death year of the directors of both films and compare them. Let's start by finding the director's name and death date for "Condemned Women".
</think>
<search>director of Condemned Women and death date</search>
<information>
  - Condemned Women (1945) was directed by Richard Wallace
  - Richard Wallace died in 1948
</information>
<think>
Now I have the death date of the director of "Condemned Women". Next, I need to find the director's name and death date for "Faces In The Dark".
</think>
<search>director of Faces In The Dark and death date</search>
<information>
  - Faces In The Dark (2014) was directed by Joshua Marston
  - Joshua Marston died in 2018
</information>
<think>
Now I have the death dates of both directors:
- Richard Wallace (Condemned Women) died in 1948
- Joshua Marston (Faces In The Dark) died in 2018

Since 1948 is earlier than 2018, the film with the director who died earlier is "Condemned Women".
</think>
<answer>
Condemned Women
</answer>
